programs - list available programs
Executable: /bin/programs.sh
Alias: programs

DESCRIPTION
  Lists all programs available
  in /bin, /rom/programs, and
  /rom/programs/fun on a single
  line.

USAGE
  programs

NOTES
  The output is written to
  /temp/ls/programs.ls and
  then printed. This replaces
  the default CraftOS 'programs'
  command with one that includes
  ReMinux's own /bin directory.

SEE ALSO
  ls - list directory contents
